{"characterId":214}],"windowDisplayName":"아스카","body":"그건 알겠는데 어떻게 멋진지가 말이야……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":214,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":214,"voiceId":"event78-01-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"그게…… 음……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event78-01-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":214}],"windowDisplayName":"아스카","body":"……아! 미안, 그런 의미가 아니라.\n아코가 어떤 걸 멋지다고 생각하는지\n알게 된다면……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":214,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":214,"voiceId":"event78-01-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":214}],"windowDisplayName":"아스카","body":"그, 아코가 말하는 Roselia의 멋짐? 이\n다른 사람한테 잘 전달되지 않을까 싶어서.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":214,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":214,"voiceId":"event78-01-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDispla